---
import site from "@/data/site.config.json"
---
<section id="inscricao" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 py-16 md:py-24" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 left-0 h-[500px] bg-gradient-to-t from-[#849CDB]/10 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="mb-8 text-center">
        <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-blood-red-800 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-white">
          Vagas Limitadas
        </span>
        <h2 id="cta-heading" class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-errie-black-900 md:text-4xl">
          Comece agora sua jornada para se tornar um
          <span class="text-[#849CDB]"> especialista em acessibilidade</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-errie-black-900/80">
          Invista nessa habilidade e faça a diferença criando experiências digitais
          inclusivas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-8 flex flex-col rounded-lg bg-blood-red-800 p-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
        <div>
          <div class="mb-2 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">R$ 1.497</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white">ou 12x de R$ 149,69 no cartão</p>
        </div>

        <a
          href={site.mentorship}
          class="mt-6 rounded-md bg-white px-8 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-blood-red-800 shadow-lg transition-colors hover:underline md:mt-0"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Garantir minha vaga
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-errie-black-900">
          Pagamento 100% seguro • Satisfação garantida ou seu dinheiro de volta em até 7 dias
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
